7 Be it enacted by the Legislature of Louisiana:
8 Section 1. R.S. 22:1034.2 is hereby enacted to read as follows:
9 §1034.2. Drug manufacturer limitations on the pricing of GLP-1 medications for
10 health insurance plans; limit on cost-sharing requirement
11 A. As used in this Section, the following terms apply:
12 (1) "Drug formulary" or "formulary" has the same meaning as provided in
13 R.S. 22:1060.1.
14 (2) "Enrollee" or "insured" has the same meaning as provided in R.S.
15 22:1872.
16 (3) "Glucagon-Like Peptide-1" known as GLP-1 means a natural gut
17 hormone that helps control blood sugar, digestion, and appetite. GLP-1 medications
18 can be injectable or administered orally, whichever form of the drug is available.
